ZH: 我的皮带是黑色的。
EN: My belt is black.

ZH: 她的皮带上有一个漂亮的金色扣子。
EN: Her belt has a beautiful golden buckle.

ZH: 这根皮带太长了，我要换一条较短的。
EN: This belt is too long, I need to exchange for a shorter one.

ZH: 我买了一条新的真皮皮带。
EN: I bought a new genuine leather belt.

ZH: 我每天都会搭配不同的皮带。
EN: I match different belts every day.

ZH: 他被皮带抽得皮开肉绽。
EN: He was whipped until his skin was ripped.

ZH: 这家店里有各式各样的皮带供选择。
EN: This store has a variety of belts to choose from.

ZH: 把皮带收拾好。
EN: Neatly put away the belt.

ZH: 她的耐克皮带很好看。
EN: Her Nike belt looks very nice.

ZH: 看，他的皮带上还有一个小口袋。
EN: Look, there is a small pocket on his belt.

ZH: 这条皮带适合我的裤子。
EN: This belt fits my pants.

ZH: 换下来的皮带可以用来修鞋。
EN: The worn-out belt can be used to fix shoes.

ZH: 我将皮带盘成一个圆圈。
EN: I looped the belt into a circle.

ZH: 这条皮带是用真皮制成的。
EN: This belt is made of genuine leather.

ZH: 他只带了一条腰带就出门了。
EN: He went out with only a belt.

ZH: 那个小男孩用皮带抽打地上。
EN: The little boy whipped the ground with a belt.

ZH: 我不懂这条皮带是什么时候露的。
EN: I don't know when this belt got exposed.

ZH: 这条皮带非常结实，撑得住很大的重量。
EN: This belt is very strong and can support a lot of weight.

ZH: 请你放下皮带，不要打人。
EN: Please put down the belt and don't hit anyone.
